headline: Businesses Focused on Navigating Uncertainty, Says Marsh McLennan CEO
summary: Marsh McLennan CEO John Doyle tells Open Interest that navigating complexity is the central concern for businesses today, particularly dealing with near-term uncertainty and managing the longer term impact of AI.
